RACE.FOOTNOTES: LOVEU AND PROUDOFU raced within striking distance, moved up on the outside around the turn, made a bid and proved the best late. MORE LIKE IT broke a step slow, raced in the back in the early going, moved up from the inside around the turn but was never a serious threat. RAP ARTIST lacked early speed and was never a factor. CHICAGO CHROME raced near the middle of the field, dropped back and was outrun. ROYAL CONSORT pressed the pace and made a steady retreat.
